{"tid":326432,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[足球撚入] 街場,friendly嘅賤人","createTime":"2017-07-18T03:58:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T05:56:00.000Z","uid":101073,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dfaf78ffe4a1a40f407efe49d21e9ce551631517","tid":326432,"uid":101073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:58:26.000Z","msg":"有無人係街場或者friendly遇過對手係明明個波係中佢出界但係死都話係中我 仲勁厚面皮拎個波翻尼開<br />\n<br />\n咁都事小 但係有少少犯規咁佢地就開晒罰球咁<br />\n佢地犯我地規呢就一腳踢個波俾我地龍門開<br />\n之後仲好似理所當然咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好黑人憎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700e3d28a49e729cf4ac82b9c65c28ac9194089f","tid":326432,"uid":101073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:02:30.000Z","msg":"其實街場同friendly大家都係想開心咁踢下波姐<br />\n無謂為左小小嘅勝利搞到自己咁肉酸呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外想問下大家對手係咁嘅人有咩方法應對"},{"pid":"07d85872643233d867a5f651db77119a47ed46f5","tid":326432,"uid":332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:16:09.000Z","msg":"唔滿意咪出聲囉，人地見你地咁好蝦緊係蝦你地啦"},{"pid":"1fa5071b22e0289e6648163bb594dc37b0d316ac","tid":326432,"uid":74851,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:17:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">尼你老母臭閪</span></span>"},{"pid":"c4dcf475c99f4ee716045d298b41589ceee0ee0e","tid":326432,"uid":52839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:18:26.000Z","msg":"街場都有罰球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a79bbe68b7aaf29e00001f811b25b3367ec323","tid":326432,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:19:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>街場都有罰球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br